I can't believe Chiguchi Miri would do this. He could've tacked on more to that three-parter he ended with a bait, but instead he's gone full chubby chaser. My disappointment is immeasurable and my day is ruined.

Man, feels like last months edition just came out. This ones pretty decent, couple NTR/ish stories in here I’m not a fan of. Chiguchi Miri’s fat girl ain’t for me personally. Nogiawa Kaede is turning into one of my favorite artists, shame their previous work hasn’t gotten translated, and this one looks even better. Airandou delivers, as always, worthy of all the praise they get. Ponsuke delivering as well, swapping usually isn’t my thing, but with Lolis, it’s a bit more tolerable. Osanp Suisou’s story was really slow, I have a feeling it’s sequel will be fantastic though. Kinomoto Anzu was okay, nothing exceptional; Maeshima Ryou much the same, decent Rape story. Kyradains stories are still too vanilla and lackluster for me, shame too, since their art is fantastic. Overall it’s above-average IMO, but not massively so 6 or 7 outta 10,  I’m not quite sure yet.  See y’all degens next month, or sooner, if we’re lucky and these get translated ;)
